    "date": "2017-11-09T17:24:05Z",
    "text": "Medical Device Safety Act\n\nThis bill amends the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to declare that an action for damages or a person's liability under state law is not affected by the federal prohibition on state or local requirements regarding medical devices. This bill is retroactively effective and applies to pending civil actions."
